== 争议 ==
有色人种进步协会形象奖因其宣称某些被提名者没有资格获得该奖而引发争议。但是，协会还认为应当按照艺人获得的成就来颁奖，至于犯罪指控之类的因素不应当左右他们的作品质量。例如，1994年，[[吐派克·夏库尔|吐派克·夏库尔]]尽管于前一年的12月即被指控对妇女性侵犯，但他还是因电影《{{link-en|恶有恶报|Poetic Justice (1993 film)}}》获得杰出电影男演员的提名。<ref>{{cite news| last = | first = | title = Michael Jackson makes surprise appearance at NAACP Image Awards| work = Jet| pages = | date = 1994-01-24| url = http://www.findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m1355/is_n12_v85/ai_14777970| accessdate = 2006-09-29| archive-date = 2009-02-20| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090220062324/http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m1355/is_n12_v85/ai_14777970| dead-url = no}}</ref>2004年，[[劳·凯利|劳·凯利]]因《Chocolate Factory》获得杰出专辑提名，<ref>{{cite web| last = Wiederhorn| first = Jon| authorlink = | title = Outkast, Beyonce, R. Kelly Nominated For NAACP Image Awards| work = VH1.com| date = 2004-01-08| url = http://www.vh1.com/artists/news/1484218/01082004/ashanti.jhtml| accessdate = 2006-09-29| archive-date = 2007-06-06| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070606181154/http://www.vh1.com/artists/news/1484218/01082004/ashanti.jhtml| dead-url = no}}</ref>而他当时因为[[儿童色情|儿童色情]]的问题官司缠身。<ref name="zahn">{{cite web| last = | first = | title = Paula Zahn Now: Can Democrats Challenge Kerry?; NAACP Controversy; California Death Penalty Debate| work = CNN.com| date = 2004-01-28| url = http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0401/28/pzn.00.html| accessdate = 2006-09-29| archive-date = 2007-05-26| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070526052709/http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0401/28/pzn.00.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>

其他被提名人常被指责是因为在作品中展现了主要民权领袖的形象而获得提名。2003年，电影《{{link-en|理发店 (电影)|Barbershop (film)|理发店}}》获得五项提名，包括杰出影片以及{{link-en|塞德里克·凯尔斯|Cedric the Entertainer}}的杰出男配角提名。但批评者认为，该电影之所以获得提名，是因为塞德里克在片中的角色明显是影射[[罗莎·帕克斯|罗莎·帕克斯]]、[[小马丁·路德·金|小马丁·路德·金]]和[[杰西·杰克逊|杰西·杰克逊]]。<ref>{{cite web| last = | first = | title = Image Awards rekindle 'Barbershop' controversy| work = CNN.com| date = 2003-03-09| url = http://www.cnn.com/2003/SHOWBIZ/TV/03/08/image.awards.ap/| accessdate = 2006-09-29| archive-date = 2006-06-29| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20060629060508/http://www.cnn.com/2003/SHOWBIZ/TV/03/08/image.awards.ap/| dead-url = no}}</ref>说唱组合[[OutKast|OutKast]]在2004年获得6项提名，也被批为是因为之前录制了一首名为《Rosa Parks》的歌曲，他们还因为此曲遭到帕克斯的起诉。<ref name="zahn"/>

